*REPOST*
If you are running IB on your local (not crafting), you need to use the redis from brew. Do:
```brew install redis
brew services start redis```
I had changed the provisioner script to remove redis in `lite` https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C06FA6A23/p1729702093178249 (Oct 23)

Reposting as I noticed that some folks didnâ€™t see the earlier post. Not having redis will make your local quite slow.
